# Simple Calculator - Python

This is a basic calculator made using Python. It performs:
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division (with zero-check)
- Exit option

## How it works

- User selects an operation by entering 1 to 5.
- Then enters two numbers.
- The result is displayed.
- Loop continues until user selects "5" to exit.

## How to Run

```bash
python main.py
